害程度、本人态度等，确保法纪效果与社会效果相统一，严格依法依规惩治违规行为。经中国象棋协会纪律与道德工作委员会研究决定，给予赵鑫鑫、汪洋、郑惟桐终身禁赛、撤销中国象棋协会技术等级称号的处罚决定。 此外，王廓、孙勇征、郝继超、党斐、崔革等 34 人被给予不同年限的禁赛处罚，另有 4 名违规人员被通报批评。又有 41 名中国象棋违规人员被处罚 赵鑫鑫等 3 人被终身禁赛"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e3bcabb06a3f5be50c666c76410ced8d_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/9389591283"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIt5a7zfe/7c0tEAMaCTExMjg1NDM1MCDbk428BjAAOHFAEHIKOTM4OTU5MTI4M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1736745756.314057", "card_id": "Q_8947756903", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 120}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "职场上，为何总说「辞职」的人没走，但毫无声响的人却走了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-51037cafa3a30d9bb17f4ab9457ba3a8_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "66 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/8947756903"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIt5a7zfe/7c0tEAMaCTExMjc2NTk5MiCOxvK7BjAAOK4BQBFyCjg5NDc3NTY5MDN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1736745756.314363", "card_id": "Q_9123096591", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 19}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么光一产生就可以达到光速，而其他物体需要不断加速？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "关于光速的说法"}, "image_area": {"